#

Truffle Mashed Potatoes

35 min
$8
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

EasyComfort FoodSide Dish

Description

Creamy, buttery mashed potatoes infused with the luxurious flavor of truffle oil.

Ingredients

  • russet potatoes: 2 pounds
  • butter: 4 tablespoons
  • heavy cream: 1/2 cup
  • truffle oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • chives (optional, for garnish): 1 tablespoon
